      "settings": {
        "title": "How to Use Your Gift Card",
        "content": "<h3>Redeeming Your Gift Card</h3><ol><li><strong>Online Shopping:</strong> Add items to cart and select 'Gift Card' at checkout. Enter your card code and PIN</li><li><strong>Physical Store:</strong> Present your card to the cashier during purchase</li><li><strong>Phone/Chat:</strong> Call or chat with our team and provide your card details</li></ol><h3>Important Details</h3><ul><li>✓ No expiry date on balance - use anytime within 2 years</li><li>✓ Can be used for products, services, delivery, installation</li><li>✓ Can combine multiple gift cards in one purchase</li><li>✓ Unused balance remains on card - no partial redemption loss</li><li>✓ Can check balance anytime on our website</li><li>✓ Non-transferable - only original recipient can use</li></ul><h3>Lost or Damaged Card?</h3><p>Contact our customer service with your card code. We'll help you recover your balance or issue a replacement card.</p>",
